   &UR; PHOTOS AND GRAPHICS: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Sergio Florez
</P>
<P>
   Phone: (888) 603-1036
</P>
<P>
   e-mail address: florez(at)nytimes.com.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; TECHNICAL PROBLEMS: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Peter Trigg
</P>
<P>
   Phone: (212) 499-3332.
</P>
<P>
   Pager: (800) 946-4645 (PIN 599-4539).
</P>
<P>
   E-mail: triggp(at)nytimes.com. &QL;
