</P>
<P>
   DEM-DONORS (Washington) _ The Democratic convention starting on
Monday in Los Angeles will be a display of wealth, power and
influence as gaudy as the Republican show in Philadelphia. By John
M. Broder and Richard A. Oppel Jr.
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 2 p.m. ET in ``p'' news file.)
