   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   CLIMBING _ It's hard to explain. Those who know don't have to
say a thing. They know, and that's enough. But occasionally
somebody asks, or the meter hits full and the feelings from on top
have nowhere to go but out. So they touch their fingertips together
to form a peak and whisper, ``Fourteener,'' a mantra of endless
meaning and possibility. (Grand Junction Daily Sentinel) MOVED.
</P>
