   WITH
</P>
<P>
   MIDWAYBIO _ At-a-glance bio box on Mark Thompson, Atlantan who
forged a one-of-a-kind agreement with U.S. Fish and Wildlife
Service to operate a eco-resort on Midway Atoll. (Pousner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution.)MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   MIDWAY-IFYOUGO _ Details on planning a trip to Midway Atoll.
(Pousner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution.)MOVED.
