<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-12 21:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9984 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BBN-MATTHEWS-LOCAL-LA     08-12 0582
